Anagram

 An anagram is a word formed by rearranging the letters of another word. For example, cinema is an anagram of iceman.
 The mechanics of the game are as follows:
 The game provides the user with a word from the dictionary.
  The user tries to create as many words as possible that contain all the letters of the given word. Note that adding the same word again will not give an angaram of the existing word.
  The user can give up and see the words that they did not guess.

